Interface SOABEModel

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
public interface SOABEModel
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'SOABE Model'. [[ TODO - add documentation here ]]

The following features are supported:

  • Base Types
  • Cod Prodotto
  • Cod Componente
  • Versione Prodotto
  • Versione Componente
  • Serviceimplementations
  • Service Defs
  • Target Platform
  • Resource Set
